            # =============================================================================

            # --- Code Block 34 ---

            # =============================================================================

            # TRANSLATION LAYER

            # Single source of truth for all user-facing text.

            # Maps internal feature names, tier codes, and quarter keys to plain English.

            # The dashboard never reads raw feature names or cluster IDs.

            # =============================================================================


